title: Arsenal Top The Table
description:
The FC crew react to Arsenal's dominate 3-0 victory over Bournemouth, question if they may have overlooked Gabriel Jesus during his time at Man City and argue if the Gunners are for real this season. Plus, the guys discuss Tottenham's win over Wolves, Real Madrid's 2nd straight LaLiga victory and recap the reactions to Casemiro's move to Manchester United.
